#- Welcome Counselor to your new digs.

This is the capitol building, ment for the seven empire counselors. 

This is your new corner office, you also have two offices adjacent to you. These are for whatever you want them to be, give them to your appointed  
#- Officials, or simple for storage. 

I hope you enjoy your new office.
#- 